data.description: A charming three bed and two bath home in Feather Ridge with mature trees in the from yard. Ceramic tiles are throughout the home along with a large kitchen, vaulted living room, spacious backyard and two car garage. Recently purchased refrigerator, washer and dryer are included.  Minutes from shopping at The Forum and Sam's Club. Also explore the nearby Retama Park, Morgan's Wonderland and sports complex, Comanche Lookout Park, and IDEA Judson charter school. Quick access to I35, Wurzbach Parkway and Loop 1604.
